snippet.title: 【English Subtitles】ReplayBellSuikaSlotLikeGame【PV1】
snippet.description:
Introducing the latest title from "Honwaka Fuwafuwa":
Here is the PV for "ReplayBellSuikaSlotLikeGame".

While it is a game similar to the so-called "Suika Game",
by generating the largest symbol, you can enter the "Live Bonus"
and experience a playstyle reminiscent of pachinko and pachislot.

Release Date: May 29, 2024
Platform: Steam
Price: $2.22

■ Store URL (Steam)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2804960/_/
Narration by: Kinomi Momo
